Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1

(6 comments)

I think you should do different things here. The whole algorithm is:
1. Get list of all supported plugins. Not just one type "Myartifact" 
2. For each plugin in the list get its name, description and displayed_name (Just take the first element in a list of installed versions and read its metadata)
2.1 Get list of installed versions of the plugin.
2.2 For each version generate its id, link and description.
3. Wrap the resulted list of plugins with the dict 'artifact_types'

Patch Set 1:

The expected result should be something like that https://etherpad.openstack.org/p/pluginVersionExample
